      - The .geoip_databases system index is visible in cat indices but direct settings access is reserved for system operations.
      - Built-in managed index templates and ILM policies are present for logs, metrics, synthetics, ML, Watcher, SLM, ILM history, and deprecation logs. No application index aliases were observed.
